    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-loved and carefully maintained car that's in great shape and ready for many more miles. While you might find a few minor cosmetic marks from regular use, it runs beautifully and offers a smooth, reliable driving experience. It's a solid, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great!",
