    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows some age with minor dings, paint fading on the hood, and a few light scratches. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will soon require a brake service and likely a new set of tires. It's a solid, functional vehicle that has been used regularly but is ready for some restorative care.",
      "price": 20500.0,
