    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical work and cosmetic restoration to become a reliable driver. The engine currently idles roughly and lacks power, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping between gears. Additionally, the body shows several dents and areas of rust that need attention. This is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or those looking for a donor vehicle for parts.",
